Problem Statement
Convert a given time from 12-hour AM/PM format to 24-hour military time.

Special cases:
12:00:00AM → 00:00:00
12:00:00PM → 12:00:00

Function Requirements
Input: A single string representing time in 12-hour format (e.g., 07:05:45PM).
Output: A string in 24-hour format (e.g., 19:05:45).

Constraints: All input times are valid.

Examples
Input: 12:01:00PM → Output: 12:01:00
Input: 12:01:00AM → Output: 00:01:00
Input: 07:05:45PM → Output: 19:05:45
